deps.context: project(bout++   description "fluid pde solver framework"   version ${bout_cmake_acceptable_version}   languages cxx)

libs.content:
find_library(netcdf_c_library
  names netcdf
  doc "netcdf c library"
  hints
    "${nc_hints_include_dir}"
    "${nc_hints_prefix}"
    "${nc_config_location}"
  path_suffixes
    "lib" "lib64"
 )

find_program(nc_config "nc-config"
  paths "${netcdf_root}"
  path_suffixes bin
  doc "path to netcdf c config helper"
  no_default_path
  )

find_library(slepc_library
    names slepc
    hints
      ${slepc_dir}/lib
      $env{slepc_dir}/lib
      ${slepc_dir}/${petsc_arch}/lib
      $env{slepc_dir}/$env{petsc_arch}/lib
    no_default_path
    doc "the slepc library")

find_library(slepc_library
    names slepc
    doc "the slepc library")

find_library(netcdf_cxx_library
  names netcdf_c++4 netcdf-cxx4
  doc "netcdf c++ library"
  hints
    "${ncxx4_hints_include_dir}"
    "${ncxx4_hints_prefix}"
    "${ncxx4_config_location}"
  path_suffixes
    "lib" "lib64"
  )

find_program(ncxx4_config "ncxx4-config"
  paths "${netcdfcxx_root}"
  path_suffixes bin
  doc "path to netcdf c++ config helper"
  no_default_path
  )

find_library(sundials_nvecparallel_library
  names sundials_nvecparallel
  hints
    "${sundials_include_dir}/.."
    "${sundials_include_dir}/../.."
  path_suffixes lib lib64
  )

find_library(sundials_${lib}_library
    names sundials_${lib}
    hints
      "${sundials_include_dir}/.."
      "${sundials_include_dir}/../.."
    path_suffixes lib lib64
    )

find_library (fftw_libraries
  names fftw3
  doc "fftw library location"
  hints "${fftw_hint_dir}"
  path_suffixes "lib" "lib64"
  )

find_program(fftw_wisdom "fftw-wisdom"
  paths "${fftw_root}"
  path_suffixes bin
  no_default_path
  doc "path to fftw-wisdom executable"
  )

find_library(hypre_library
  names hypre
  doc "hypre library"
  required
  path_suffixes lib64 lib
  )

find_program(sphinx_executable
             names sphinx-build sphinx-build-3
             doc "path to sphinx-build executable")

deps.context: project(pvode   description "ode solver"   version 0.1   languages cxx)
